    "Considering the aforementioned concerns, it is unambiguous that there is a need to make profound changes in Academic Writing courses to capture students' attention and increase their attention span in the Iraq context.",
    "In this regard, employing PBL is recognized as a game changer to transform their writing performance and motivation, thereby breaking the monotonous negative cycle in Academic Writing settings.",
    "Correspondingly, this study seeks to address the following research questions:",
    "• How effective is PBL to improve students' writing performance in Academic Writing courses?",
    "• What is the influence of PBL in boosting students' motivation in Academic Writing courses?"
